{"id":629,"date":"2020-08-13T02:10:01","date_gmt":"2020-08-12T19:10:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?page_id=629"},"modified":"2024-10-18T15:09:43","modified_gmt":"2024-10-18T08:09:43","slug":"reflections-restaurant","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/reflections-restaurant\/","title":{"rendered":"Reflections Restaurant"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47ka1tcc fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/ref-web-5-1.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/bbb3fc4e490bb73216342926df1bf77e_ref-web-5-1-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/bbb3fc4e490bb73216342926df1bf77e_ref-web-5-1-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/bbb3fc4e490bb73216342926df1bf77e_ref-web-5-1-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/bbb3fc4e490bb73216342926df1bf77e_ref-web-5-1-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/ref-web-5-1.jpg\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-47liksft fg-section fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-47liksfu fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47liksg3 fg-image  img-responsive fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/b598c739837858f264fe42f99107a46f_Logo-Reflections-Restaurant-300-c-90.png\"><div class=\"ffb-id-47liksg4 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">A fine-dining restaurant with a cosmopolitan outlook, Reflections&rsquo; award-winning team is dedicated to serving creative dishes from around the world to diners in the heart of Saigon.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Guest chef appearances, wine dinners, and workshops are a few of the ways Reflections advances the city&rsquo;s culinary ambitions. Every two months the restaurant drafts a new menu of specials starring the best seasonal produce sourced from around the globe. While taking inspiration from international cooking styles and techniques, Reflections&rsquo; gives an unmistakable nod to its Vietnamese setting, using local, organically grown fruits and vegetables.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Claiming a discreet perspective above one of the city&rsquo;s most prominent intersections, this third-floor restaurant is a fitting space to reflect on the changing faces of Vietnam. Photographs on the walls pay tribute to Saigon&rsquo;s heritage, and patrons have a front row view of the lights of Lam Son Square and the Saigon Opera House. Enhanced by the warm, intuitive service the Caravelle is known for, Reflections aims to create a magical, memorable dining experience every time.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">24-hour In room Wining &amp; Dining is always ready to ensure guest's convenience and experience.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">__________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">3rd Floor. 17:30 &ndash; 22:00<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Reflections Restaurant opens daily<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">__________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Business-class Luncheon is available everyday, from 11:00 &ndash; 14:00<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">__________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Reflections' Dress Code:<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Smart Casual. Strictly no singlets, workout attire, flip flops<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">__________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">For more information, please contact (84) 2838 234 999 or email: culinary@